sourcesContent:
import React from "react"; import "./StudentDetails.css" const StudentDetails = ({ student }) => { if (!student) return null; // If there's no student, return nothing return (

Student Details

ENO: {student.eno}

Name: {student.name}

Course: {student.course}

Email: {student.email}

Phone: {student.phno}

Date of Birth: {new Date(student.dob).toLocaleDateString()}

Gender: {student.gender}

Batch: {student.batch}

Address

Block Number: {student.address.blockNum}

Building Name: {student.address.buildingName}

Area: {student.address.area}

Landmark: {student.address.landmark}

Pincode: {student.address.pincode}

City: {student.address.city}

State: {student.address.state}

Educational Details

SSC

Marks: {student.ssc.marks} / {student.ssc.totalMarks}

Percentage: {student.ssc.percentage}%

Year: {student.ssc.year}

Board: {student.ssc.board}

HSC

Marks: {student.hsc.marks} / {student.hsc.totalMarks}

Percentage: {student.hsc.percentage}%

Stream: {student.hsc.stream}

Board: {student.hsc.board}

Year: {student.hsc.year}

Bachelor's Degree

Marks: {student.bachelor.marks} / {student.bachelor.totalMarks}

Percentage: {student.bachelor.percentage}%

Degree: {student.bachelor.degree}

University: {student.bachelor.university}

Year: {student.bachelor.year}

Master's Degree

Marks: {student.master.marks} / {student.master.totalMarks}

Percentage: {student.master.percentage}%

Degree: {student.master.degree}

University: {student.master.university}

Year: {student.master.year}

Other Information

Lateral Entry: {student.lEntry ? "Yes" : "No"}

Drops: {student.drops}

Remarks: {student.remarks}

); }; export default StudentDetails;
